#!/bin/bash
# export MD_NOTEBOOKS_DIR in your bashrc or zshrc to the directory you cloned md-notebooks
# Usage: tn {tool}
# example: tn bash
TOOL=${1}
if [[ -z ${TOOL} ]]; then
  ls -1 ${MD_NOTEBOOKS_DIR}/Tools_Notes/
else
  mdcat "$MD_NOTEBOOKS_DIR/Tools_Notes/$1/"$(ls "$MD_NOTEBOOKS_DIR/Tools_Notes/$1" | fzf )
fi
